high_descs: Turn left and walk straight past the fridge, then turn left and face the counter.
Pick up the spoon.
Turn right and walk past the stove.
Put the spoon in the brown mug.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around and walk straight to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink to the left of everything else.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around into the kitchen to face the counter right of the fridge
Pick up the spoon from the counter
Walk over to the right of the stove
Put the spoon into the orange mug on the counter
Pick up the mug from the counter
Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink
Put the mug into the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with spoon into the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the counter next to the fridge.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Approach the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the spoon in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: go to your left then then left again to the counter with the skillet and utensils on it
pick up the spoon from the counter
turn to your right and go towards the stove top
place the spoon in the orange bowl that is to the right of the stove top
pick up the orange bowl with the spoon in it
turn around and go to your right towards the white sink
stop at the sink and place the bowl and spoon in the sink in the upper left hand corner
anns.task_desc: find a bowl and spoon and place them in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and move to the small counter between the stove and the fridge.
There is a spoon on the counter.  Pick it up.
Turn to the left and move to the small counter on the right side of the stove.
There are many items, but you need to pick up the brown bowl.
Put the spoon in the bowl.
Turn around and cross the room until you reach the sink.
Place the bowl and spoon in the sink.
